
    <div class="container-fluid banner">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="entry-form">
            <form action="/reflections" method="POST">

                <h1 class="title">Student Project Reflection</h1>
                <hr>
                <p>Welcome! Time to give your teacher some feedback about your project.</p>

                <div class="form-group">

                <label>What Is Your Name?</label><br>
                <input class="form-control" name="student_name" size="50" id="name" type="text" placeholder="Mary Jane Student" required>
                <br>
                <label>Which Block Do You Belong To?</label><br>
                <input class="form-control" size="50" name="block" id="block" type="text" placeholder="Block 1" required>
                <br>
                <label>Who Is Your Teacher?</label><br>
                <input class="form-control" name="teacher_name" size="50" id="teacher_name" type="text" placeholder="Ms. Smarty" required>
                <br>
                <label>What Is the Name of This Project?</label><br>
                <input class="form-control" name="project_name" size="50" id="project_name" type="text" placeholder="Book Report" required>
                <br>

                <p>Which kind of project is this?
                    <select class="form-control" name="project_type" id="dropdown" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="Independent project">Independent project</option>
                        <option value="Partner project">Partner project</option>
                        <option value="Triad project">Triad project</option>
                        <option value="Quad project">Quad project</option>
                        <option value="Other">Other</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>Rate the following areas.</p>
                <p>Conduct:
                    <select class="form-control" name="conduct" id="conduct" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="No Expectations Followed">No Expectations Followed</option>
                        <option value="Expectations Inconsistently Followed">Expectations Inconsistently Followed</option>
                        <option value="Expectations Consistently Followed">Expectations Consistently Followed</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>Leadership Abilities:
                    <select class="dropdown form-control" name="leadership" id="leadership" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="No Expectations Followed">No Expectations Followed</option>
                        <option value="Expectations Inconsistently Followed">Expectations Inconsistently Followed</option>
                        <option value="Expectations Consistently Followed">Expectations Consistently Followed</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>Work Requirements:
                    <select class="dropdown form-control" name="work" id="work" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="Missed 3 or more requirements">Missed 3 or more requirements</option>
                        <option value="Missed 1 or 2 requirements">Missed 1 or 2 requirements</option>
                        <option value="Met all requirements">Met all requirements</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>Creativity:
                    <select class="dropdown form-control" name="creativity" id="creativity" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="Poor">Poor</option>
                        <option value="Fair">Fair</option>
                        <option value="Good">Good</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>Collaboration:
                    <select class="dropdown form-control" name="collaboration" id="collaboration" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="Poor">Poor</option>
                        <option value="Fair">Fair</option>
                        <option value="Good">Good</option>
                    </select>
                </p>


                <p>Critical Thinking:
                    <select class="dropdown form-control" name="thinking" id="thinking" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="Poor">Poor</option>
                        <option value="Fair">Fair</option>
                        <option value="Good">Good</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>Communication:
                    <select class="dropdown form-control" name="communication" id="communication" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Select your option</option>
                        <option value="Poor">Poor</option>
                        <option value="Fair">Fair</option>
                        <option value="Good">Good</option>
                    </select>
                </p>

                <p>What did you like most about the project? What did you dislike most about it? Do you have any comments or suggestions? Be sure to keep your remarks courteous.</p>
                <textarea name="comments" id="comments" class="form-control comments" rows="6" cols="60" placeholder="Tell us more!"></textarea>
                <br>
                <button class="submit" id="submit" type="submit">Submit</button>
                <br><br>
                <a href="/users/show">Never mind. Cancel this and take me back to the list.</a>
                </div>

            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
